  "text": "In the present study, we analyzed a cohort of 130 AgP patients and 339 appropriate periodontally healthy control individuals and genotyped the four tagging SNPs (rs2891168, rs1333042, rs1333048 and rs496892) that had been associated with AgP by [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Our AgP patient cohort comprised exclusively individuals with gAgP. Patients suffering from this most severe form of AgP showed the strongest association findings in the study of Schaefer and co-workers [CITATION_3] , and therefore, our cohort, exhibiting a similar size as the gAgP cohort in their study, should be adequately suited to confirm their results.",
